snippet.title: Still Wakes the Deep - Official Behind the Scenes Trailer | IGN Fan Fest 2024
snippet.description:
1975. Disaster strikes the Beira D oil rig off the coast of Scotland. Navigate the collapsing rig to save your crew from an otherworldly horror on the edge of all logic and reality. Still Wakes the Deep is coming to Xbox, PlayStation, and PC.

#IGNFanFest
